  "firstMessage": {
   "id": 3457323,
   "postDate": "2026-05-13T15:01:48.467Z",
   "rawMarkdown": "I am so excited and impressed by Codex GPT5.5 that I have to share what Codex did for me yesterday!\n\nYesterday, I rented a cloud virtual machine with public ip address. I then gave the root password to Codex and asked Codex to SSH into the machine and install a web server and build a web gui so I can view ARC-AGI puzzles and create ONNX by hand with a GUI. In a few minutes, Codex made a working web page with GUI for me to make ONNX by hand.\n\nThis is absolutely amazing. Whatever we can imagine, LLM's can make for us in minutes. I can now visit my webpage, make ONNX and download the onnx files and include in my Kaggle submissions. Wow wow wow!\n\n(And the GUI is incredibly good. I click to add nodes. I can move them around and connect them to other nodes. And i can click on them and configure their parameters. I can then run them and see the output grids and make changes so they solve the puzzles!)\n\n![](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/cdeotte/Kaggle_Images/refs/heads/main/May-2026/webgui.png)",
   "content": "<p>I am so excited and impressed by Codex GPT5.5 that I have to share what Codex did for me yesterday!</p>\n<p>Yesterday, I rented a cloud virtual machine with public ip address. I then gave the root password to Codex and asked Codex to SSH into the machine and install a web server and build a web gui so I can view ARC-AGI puzzles and create ONNX by hand with a GUI. In a few minutes, Codex made a working web page with GUI for me to make ONNX by hand.</p>\n<p>This is absolutely amazing. Whatever we can imagine, LLM's can make for us in minutes. I can now visit my webpage, make ONNX and download the onnx files and include in my Kaggle submissions. Wow wow wow!</p>\n<p>(And the GUI is incredibly good. I click to add nodes. I can move them around and connect them to other nodes. And i can click on them and configure their parameters. I can then run them and see the output grids and make changes so they solve the puzzles!)</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/cdeotte/Kaggle_Images/refs/heads/main/May-2026/webgui.png\" alt=\"\"></p>",
   "parent": {},
